@Initial revision
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: cardslot.c,v 1.2 2002/03/14 01:26:53 millert Exp $ */
/*	$NetBSD: cardslot.c,v 1.9 2000/03/22 09:35:06 haya Exp $	*/

